snippet.title: Best VGM 2245 - Dragon Ball Xenoverse 2 - Character Creation Theme
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PS4 / XB1 / Switch / PC
Dragon Ball Xenoverse 2 (2016)
Character Creation Theme
Yoshichika Kuriyama, Shiho Terada, Atusushi Yokoseki & Steve Aoki

Twitter: https://twitter.com/SupraDarky
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SupraDarky
Bandcamp: https://supradarky.bandcamp.com/
Steam: https://steamcommunity.com/id/SupraDarky
